{"tid":1229411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"誰是殺人兇手？","createTime":"2019-06-16T02:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:13:10.000Z","uid":262576,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1263afad3c7364784d2fef522e881b5652b1488","tid":1229411,"uid":262576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"法網狙擊第五集<br />\n<br />\n劇中引述一案例<br />\n<br />\n2002年香港<br />\n一個嗜賭的男子，<br />\n欠下高利貸一筆錢，<br />\n他沒有錢還，所以四處躲避，<br />\n他多次被收高利貸的抓到毆打警告，<br />\n最後一次，<br />\n他嚇得躲在女朋友的屋子裡，<br />\n兩個收高利貸的男子帶著汽油鐵鍊，<br />\n上門要脅說燒死他，<br />\n他很害怕在無路逃之際，<br />\n他惟有爬窗逃走 結果跌死<br />\n後來法庭判兩名男子誤殺罪名成立<br />\n法庭相信，那兩名男子真的會放火傷害死者<br />\n造成死者墜樓的原因"},{"pid":"f064a3bae8af116afe592b2b20debeee0654a2e4","tid":1229411,"uid":262576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"445e91ea33b00cd1415dc11d50a6fbb2677a7fdf","tid":1229411,"uid":262576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f00dd5e668fda7a46bd4d7c3d5b431c99500e8d7","tid":1229411,"uid":262576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9644b761a410f990ca948d813eafb71ce4f40888","tid":1229411,"uid":262576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e84c700f5bc05813dd2540d565de27d8488de7e","tid":1229411,"uid":208931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4154378165de9f7b07522e978ff94fcbce9ae768","tid":1229411,"uid":208931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"政治逼人走上絕路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a1e1cd76a85140920fa4d7835ac223a82b0bbb","tid":1229411,"uid":208931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr